	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-32749" number="38808" version="3">
			<HEADING>Chapter 15: Residential Enforcement Routing</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-4363" name="T16C015"/>Chapter 15: Residential Enforcement Routing</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-32750" number="38809" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 15-01 Designation of Enforcement Routing Hours for Residential Buildings.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-4365" name="T16C015_15-01"/>§ 15-01 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Designation of Enforcement Routing Hours for Residential Buildings.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-32751" number="38810" version="2512">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Purpose.</CHARFORMAT> The purpose of this chapter is to designate two (2) one-hour periods each day when the Department will conduct citywide enforcement routing for residential premises pursuant to § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-118.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-118.1</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-32752" number="38811" version="1825">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Definition.</CHARFORMAT> For purposes of this chapter, &quot;citywide enforcement routing for residential premises&quot; means enforcement by authorized Department representatives of subdivision two of § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-118" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-118</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York, as such subdivision relates to cleaning of sidewalks, flagging, curbstones and roadway areas by owners, lessees, tenants, occupants or persons in charge of residential premises.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-32753" number="38812" version="2313">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Hours of Residential Enforcement Routing.</CHARFORMAT> The Department establishes the periods from 8:00 a.m. to 9:00 a.m. and from 6:00 p.m. to 7:00 p.m. as the two (2) one-hour periods during which time the Department will conduct citywide enforcement routing for residential premises.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-32754" number="38813" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 15-02 Applicability.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-4367" name="T16C015_15-02"/>§ 15-02 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Applicability.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-32755" number="38814" version="1825">
									<PARA>This chapter shall apply only to residential premises and shall not apply to commercial premises. The schedule for citywide enforcement routing for commercial premises in effect as of the effective date of this chapter shall continue in effect until such time as such schedule is changed by the Department in accordance with § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-118.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-118.1</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>